
Miscellaneous processor related functions are available in the
@code{<hexo/cpu.h>} header file.

These functions include:

@itemize
@item Processor related intialization functions presented in @xref{System startup}.
@findex cpu_get_cls
@item @code{void *cpu_get_cls(cpu_id_t cpu_id)} function returns the processor local storage pointer.
@findex cpu_id
@tindex cpu_id_t
@item @code{cpu_id_t cpu_id(void)} function returns the processor id.
@findex cpu_isbootstrap
@item @code{bool_t cpu_isbootstrap(void)} function can be used to check if code is running on the bootstrap processor.
@findex arch_get_cpu_count
@item @code{cpu_id_t arch_get_cpu_count(void)} function returns the total processor count.
@findex cpu_cycle_count
@tindex cpu_cycle_t
@item @code{cpu_cycle_t cpu_cycle_count()} function returns the processor time stamp counter if available.
@end itemize

